  "description": {
    "en": {
      "provenance": "imported",
      "value": "Community mobilisation in 7 communities;\r\n\tOrganised and evaluated capacity development training on financial literacy and good governance in 7 communities;\r\n\tCommissioned 6 community owned bio-gas system in 6 community;\r\n\tResearch completed on the potential of large scale Bag-Digester in Nepal;\r\n\tInstalled and tested one large scale of Bag-digester in 1 community;\r\n\t14 operator appointed and capacitated in operation and maintenance training;\r\n\t50% of the total beneficiaries capacitated in enterprise development and more than two enterprises establised in each project site;\r\n\t50% of adolescents in two communities capacitated in livelihood and enterprise development;\r\n\tSustainability report produced; and\r\n\tProject monitoring and program evaluation report produced and sahred with all stakeholders;"
    },
